lyrics:
[Verse]
In the land of the stars, on the shores of the west
I found a girl whose beauty outshone the rest
From across the ocean, her heart's melody called
But destiny's cruel hand ensured we would be stalled

[Chorus]
Oh, girl from America, why'd you steal my heart away
Now I'm left here longing, yearning for another day
But the miles between us only grow stronger, it seems
Oh, girl from America, you're forever in my dreams
